name: IteratorUtils_toListTest
description: Unit tests for the IteratorUtils.toList method.

test_cases.name: testToList_SuccessfulConversion
test_cases.description: Tests the successful conversion of an iterator to a list.

test_cases.name: testToList_NullIterator
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of the toList method when a null iterator is provided, expecting a NullPointerException.

test_cases.name: testToList_InvalidEstimatedSize
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of the toList method when an invalid estimated size is provided, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.
